Feline::

She got up onto her knees and looked at the three.  Her skin was no 
longer on her body. She was all in crome now.  She was in bot 
mode. "I, I don't feel very well."
She knew how to act to gain symapthy from other bots, but for once, 
it wasn't an act.  She looked at herself. "I'm, I've, I have no 
skin." she looked at the pile of ragged leopard pelt on the 
ground. "I lost my beast mode, or at least the most important part. 
What do I do now?"
